(after you shot him the back, your turned around to fire at Rex. But 
forget it, it's too late now. Just to say that my the beginning of my 
post stands, where Octociz talked to him, but now I'm changing the 
ending.)

Bronco crawled a few yards away, to get out of the range of fire. He 
sat, hiding behind a tree, watching, filling up his rage. He used his 
special tactic: He merged his two rocket launchers together to make 
one with a scope and tracking powers.

This one can't miss, he thought.

He aimed right at the bots head, being silent as ever, and fired.
